Package: baskoptr
Title: Utility-based Optimization for Basket Trial Designs
Version: 1.0.0
Description: The goal of baskoptr is to supply a unified framework for optimizing
    basket trial designs. To this end, the package supplies several utility
    functions and also a function for executing optimization algorithms on basket
    trial designs.
